Usage: lunchtoast <test-path> [params] [flags] 
Arguments:
    <test-path> (path)      
Parameters:
   -r, --report <path>      save test report to file
                              (optional, default: "")
   -e, --ext <string>       the extension of searched test files, required 
                              when specified test path is a directory
                              (optional, default: .toast)
   -w, --width <int>        set test report's width in number of characters
                              (optional, default: 48)
       --shell <string>     shell command
                              (optional, default: sh -c -e)
Flags:
   -s, --save-contents      save the current contents of of the test directory
       --no-cleanup         cleanup test files
       --help               show usage info and exit

